:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:46:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nikolayyordanov\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ba7ade3c5276591a8dd38047a89f1de7?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:16:\"Nikolay Yordanov\";}s:7:\"codente\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:38:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/codente\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2da21f257e56c57525ce4402ce9bf246?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:5:\"Jamie\";}s:5:\"pross\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:36:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pross\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/df9c761356c574b3fd5042db3273e438?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:13:\"Simon Prosser\";}s:13:\"pedromendonca\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pedromendonca\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/39736018b4d3a3c544db97a780167af9?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:15:\"Pedro Mendonça\";}s:9:\"dannyholt\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:40:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dannyholt\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/41d26478cda2e6cab64a608ed4c961c0?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:5:\"Danny\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.6\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"5.3.2\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"5.6\";s:6:\"rating\";i:96;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:302;i:4;i:8;i:3;i:2;i:2;i:4;i:1;i:7;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:323;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:7;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:6;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:400000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2020-01-08 7:56pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2014-11-04\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:107:\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/?utm_medium=bb&utm_source=plugins-admin-page&utm_campaign=plugins-admin-uri\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:5785:\"<h4>What Is The Beaver Builder Page Builder?</h4>\n<p>Beaver Builder is a flexible drag and drop page builder that works on the front end of your WordPress website. Whether you&#8217;re a beginner or a professional, you&#8217;re going to love taking control of your website. Stop writing HTML or wrestling with confusing shortcodes. With Beaver Builder, building beautiful, professional WordPress pages is as easy as dragging and dropping.</p>\n<p>Watch the video below or <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/go/demo?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-demo-link\" title=\"Beaver Builder Live Demo\" rel=\"nofollow\">try out the demo</a> to see it in action!</p>\n<div class=\"embed-vimeo\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/122546222\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Premium Support</strong></p>\n<p>The Beaver Builder team provides very limited support on the WordPress.org forums. Please feel free to post questions or bug reports, but for <em>timely</em> support, we recommend purchasing a Beaver Builder license.</p>\n<p>Along with access to our expert support team, there are many time-saving features in the premium versions which make it a great value for any serious WordPress user. <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/pricing/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-support-cta\" title=\"Beaver Builder Premium Support\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Get a license today.</strong></a></p>\n<p>You can also reference our <a href=\"https://kb.wpbeaverbuilder.com/\" title=\"Beaver Builder Knowledge Base\" rel=\"nofollow\">Knowledge Base</a>, or try asking the Beaver Builder community for help in either <a href=\"http://beaver.builders/wp-repo-fb\" title=\"Beaver Builders on Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> or <a href=\"http://beaver.builders/wp-repo-slack\" title=\"Beaver Builders on Slack\" rel=\"nofollow\">Slack</a>. Keep in mind, these are all folks just like you who are volunteering their time.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4>Join our Growing Community</h4>\n<p>There is a huge colony (<em>yeah, that&#8217;s the term for a group of beavers</em>) of &#8220;Beaver Builders&#8221; that would love to get to know you! If you have questions, a project to show off, or you would like to meet and network with other Beaver Builder users, you&#8217;ll feel right at home in the <a href=\"http://beaver.builders/wp-repo-fb\" title=\"Beaver Builders on Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beaver Builders Facebook Group</a> or the <a href=\"http://beaver.builders/wp-repo-slack\" title=\"Beaver Builders on Slack\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beaver Builders Slack Channel</a>. Come on by and say hello.</p>\n<h4>Page Builder Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Content Modules: HTML, Photo, Text Editor, Audio, Video, &amp; Sidebar.</li>\n<li>Full-width, column-based layouts.</li>\n<li>Lightweight and semantic markup for maximum performance.</li>\n<li>Photo, color, and video row backgrounds.</li>\n<li>Mobile-friendly, responsive layouts.</li>\n<li>Add your own CSS classes and IDs.</li>\n<li>Use WordPress Widgets and shortcodes.</li>\n<li>Works with Pages, Posts, and Custom Post Types.</li>\n<li>A friendly and supportive community.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Premium Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Additional modules: Contact Form, Tabs, Slider, Pricing Table, Map, Blog Posts, Subscribe Form, Social Icons, and many more.</li>\n<li>Expert support from our world-class support team.</li>\n<li>Beautiful pre-made layout templates.</li>\n<li>Save, export, and reuse full-page layouts, rows, and modules.</li>\n<li>Build your own custom modules.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Come by <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-homepage-link\" title=\"Beaver Builder Homepage\" rel=\"nofollow\">the Beaver Builder Homepage</a> to learn more about what our premium features can do for you!</p>\n<h4>People REALLY LOVE Beaver Builder</h4>\n<p>Don&#8217;t just take our word for it, here are a few testimonials from happy users and customers.</p>\n<p>&#8220;Simply put, it is the best page builder in the WordPress ecosystem. There is no close second.&#8221; &#8211; WP Crafter</p>\n<p>&#8220;Complete design freedom with no coding and it is all fully responsive as well.&#8221; &#8211; skyboro</p>\n<p>&#8220;Easy to use, fast to get started, real product depth, great support.&#8221; &#8211; David Bressler</p>\n<h4>Modules And Widgets</h4>\n<p>We&#8217;ve loaded Beaver Builder up with a flexible set of content modules to aid you in building stunning layouts and landing pages within an intuitive drag and drop system. Beaver Builder also supports core and third party WordPress widgets and shortcodes, so you can use Beaver Builder with all your <em>other</em> favorite plugins!</p>\n<h4>A WordPress Page Builder That Works With Your Theme</h4>\n<p>Yep, that&#8217;s right! Beaver Builder was designed to work with almost any WordPress theme. Try Beaver Builder on your existing website today, or consider upgrading and using Beaver Builder&#8217;s outstanding framework theme (available in Pro and Agency packages) for your next project.</p>\n<h4>A WordPress Page Builder That&#8217;s 100% Mobile Friendly</h4>\n<p>Every part of a Beaver Builder layout or landing page is fully responsive and looks gorgeous on any screen size. Responsive web design has never been easier.</p>\n<h4>A WordPress Page Builder That&#8217;s Optimized For Performance</h4>\n<p>We&#8217;ve designed Beaver Builder to create layouts and landing pages that load quickly. Many page builders load in an ungodly number of scripts and stylesheets to every page on your site. Not Beaver Builder! It only loads the assets needed for a given layout or landing page.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:912:\"<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Install Beaver Builder either via the WordPress plugin directory or by uploading the files to your server at wp-content/plugins.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>After activating Beaver Builder, navigate to the settings page at Settings &gt; Page Builder to configure the post types you would like it to work with.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>A <em>Page Builder</em> tab will appear on the Edit Page/Post area. Also, a <em>Page Builder</em> option will appear in the WordPress Admin Bar on the front end of your website.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>For more information, please visit our <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/documentation/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-install-kb-link\" title=\"Beaver Builder Knowledge Base\" rel=\"nofollow\">Knowledge Base</a>. Keep in mind that not all features described in the knowledge base are available in this version of the Beaver Builder plugin.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:587:\"<p>For information on using Beaver Builder, please visit our <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/knowledge-base/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-faq-kb-link\" title=\"Beaver Builder Knowledge Base\" rel=\"nofollow\">Knowledge Base</a>.</p>\n<p>For general questions or questions about purchasing a license, check out our <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/frequently-asked-questions/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-faq-link\" title=\"Beaver Builder FAQs\" rel=\"nofollow\">Frequently Asked Questions</a> page.</p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:315:\"<p>Visit our <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/change-logs/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-changelog-page\" title=\"Beaver Builder Changelog\" rel=\"nofollow\">changelog page</a> for up-to-date information on what has been going on with the development of Beaver Builder.</p>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:1109:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1372383\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1372383\" alt=\"Starting Beaver Builder from the backend.\"></a><p>Starting Beaver Builder from the backend.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1372383\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1372383\" alt=\"Starting Beaver Builder from the front end.\"></a><p>Starting Beaver Builder from the front end.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1372383\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1372383\" alt=\"The main editing interface.\"></a><p>The main editing interface.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=1372383\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=1372383\" alt=\"Editing basic text.\"></a><p>Editing basic text.</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:17113:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Made my site + fantastic support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alisontestroete\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/57fa84a9608622e753c8b6dc05a2f610?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/57fa84a9608622e753c8b6dc05a2f610?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alisontestroete\" class=\"reviewer-name\">alisonbike <small>(alisontestroete)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 6, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">As a novice to WordPress, I took the advice to use beaver builder. I couldn\'t be happier with the results. The support team saved me countless hours and money with their very responsive help. 120% recommended.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">I Love Using Beaver Builder</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brian1773\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4ebb2dc4eb92d18074077bc025524823?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4ebb2dc4eb92d18074077bc025524823?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brian1773\" class=\"reviewer-name\">brian1773</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 16, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">They have changed the way I think about building websites forever. It gives you the ability to have all the backend power and customizability of Wordpress with the ease of use of something like Wix or Squarespace but with way more control of the content\'s appearance on different device sizes without needing to know any coding.\n\nThere is a setting for just about anything you could want to do especially if you use the Beaver Themer add-on plugin that they offer. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">I&#039;m still waiting</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cameron816\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae1118c7ab34ee3048c618139166a8d8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae1118c7ab34ee3048c618139166a8d8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cameron816\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cameron816</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have managed WP, with the Beaver Builder lite version available. But it never worked, the page builder tabs aren\'t visible, only launch Beaver Builder, or use blocks. So I upgraded and that BB version doesn\'t have the page builder tabs, my managed WP still only has the launch BB button, that leads you right back to the BB upsell page. \n\nI\'ve complained, tried to get support, but I hear it\'s Go Daddy, Go Daddy is saying no it BB issue. WP told me that it\'s BB they don\'t have anything to do with plug in. Frankly, I\'m unimpressed with the support or product. Until I see support my rating will stay low. there are other drag and drop plug ins that would provide the same drag and drop as BB, and maybe provide better support. Hell, I\'ve received emails from BB saying they could log in, what\'s the problem, yet when I go to log in, the very same issues exist. Essentially in the nut shell, I\'ve paid for a service that I\'ve never received, I\'ve asked for support, I\'ve received nothing of substance, just emails saying we don\'t see anything wrong.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Love the Product. GREAT SUPPORT</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wkcollins\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/52daac330915bfc7d67a02beaf8dbe7b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/52daac330915bfc7d67a02beaf8dbe7b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wkcollins\" class=\"reviewer-name\">wkcollins</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 9, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">BB and Themer have been a life-changer for me. I getting some really good sites launched in record time, which is making me more profitable. Support is awesome too. I thought I had an issue with Themer. Turned out not to be Themer related, and support help me fix the issue anyway. Much appreciated.  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Love it! So easy, just works</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cleanerorc\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1ee292fdc7d9decd49ac21fd43f24108?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1ee292fdc7d9decd49ac21fd43f24108?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cleanerorc\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cleanerorc</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 20, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Been using BB for a week now and after a couple days I decided to buy the premium version because what I saw was solid and much easier GUI than several other builders I\'d tried.\n\nSubsequently I had a couple issues that I contacted BB support about, and both turned out to be errors generated by 3rd part plugins.\n\nIn addition to enjoying the easy user interface, I just wanted to add this review even though I\'m a new user, since support in both cases has responded and fixed the issues like by next morning.\n\nTry it you\'ll like it!!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">The best builder plugin available</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rwilki\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/407ed597fc7fdf85ed210108aabe02a8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/407ed597fc7fdf85ed210108aabe02a8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rwilki\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rwilki</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 17, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been using Beaver Builder (thanks to Chris Lema\'s recommendation) for a long time. Recently, I upgraded to the Pro version, but only for specific reasons. The Builder Lite version is perfect for most sites. It\'s fast, easy to train people on and just plain predictable — meaning stable. Support is incredible too. I won\'t use another builder plugin if I don\'t have to.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plugin and Awesome Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pete_gregory\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e4254356fa9b8f402292dbf33dbc1719?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e4254356fa9b8f402292dbf33dbc1719?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pete_gregory\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pete_gregory</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 9, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been using the BB theme and plugins for a couple years now and my experience has been outstanding. The devs are a wonderful bunch and I\'ve had very few problems, never anything major. Of course, I have an Agency license and the few times I\'ve needed support, it\'s been a positive experience. They really do go the extra mile to help out, even when it turns out not to be their issue. Since I have a good understanding of CSS, I never thought I\'d take to using a page builder. I expected it to slow the site down, but I\'ve learned it\'s actually the opposite. I swear, pages I build with BB are faster than pages I design and code myself. How do they do that, I don\'t know, but you can\'t go wrong with Beaver Builder. I recommend all the Beaver Builder products, 100%.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">An over all good plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/venkatapardhasaradhi\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8dbd4560d6cd98213a309422ad2fa731?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8dbd4560d6cd98213a309422ad2fa731?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/venkatapardhasaradhi\" class=\"reviewer-name\">venkatapardhasaradhi</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 7, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I am using this plugin form a year. Works well and had no glitches so far. The only downside I could think of it is, the number of modules is far less compared with other page/theme builder plugins.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Must have plugin!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jholecek\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1e3c9f429e71e8ba27eaa627b078bf51?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1e3c9f429e71e8ba27eaa627b078bf51?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jholecek\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jholecek</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 18, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'m new to WordPress and quickly discovered that I needed a builder to create a site quickly and easily. Beaver Builder light is included with GoDaddy WordPress. Before deciding to go with the paid upgrade, I researched builder reviews, and the good press Beaver Builder received convinced me to go with the upgrade, and am I EVER HAPPY that I did. Not only is the product super good, the support is unbelievably good. The support alone is worth buying the product. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">My Trusted Website Builder</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/craignic17\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5b34b10bff53cb7016df684e9a7d0513?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5b34b10bff53cb7016df684e9a7d0513?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/craignic17\" class=\"reviewer-name\">craignic17</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 29, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Beaver Builder is now the only tool I use to create Wordpress websites. I love it because it\'s easy to use and I can use my creativity to build any custom website.\nOn its own, Beaver Builder is maybe a little basic, so I recommend using Beaver Themer and Ultimate Addons.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:70:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:80:\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1372383\";s:7:\"caption\";s:41:\"Starting Beaver Builder from the backend.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:80:\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1372383\";s:7:\"caption\";s:43:\"Starting Beaver Builder from the front end.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:80:\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1372383\";s:7:\"caption\";s:27:\"The main editing interface.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:80:\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=1372383\";s:7:\"caption\";s:19:\"Editing basic text.\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:14:\"beaver-builder\";s:14:\"beaver builder\";s:20:\"drag-and-drop-editor\";s:20:\"Drag And Drop editor\";s:17:\"front-end-builder\";s:17:\"front-end builder\";s:12:\"landing-page\";s:12:\"landing page\";s:12:\"page-builder\";s:12:\"page builder\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:84:{s:6:\"1.10.4\";s:77:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.4.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.5.1\";s:79:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.5.1.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.6.3